{"tid":1290762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚所有曾經向康文署投訴屯門大媽嘅巴絲","createTime":"2019-07-06T15:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T16:06:15.000Z","uid":188104,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"80001bf3807c02b5ff435bb5f94cf58d74a7cd28","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:17:02.000Z","msg":"如果各位巴絲曾經向康文署投訴屯門大媽<br />\n而覺得康文署無解決到問題<br />\n就可以向申訴專員公署投訴康文署<br />\n<br />\n就算康文署有去處理大家投訴<br />\n但個情況都無改善<br />\n申訴都一定受理<br />\n而且一定做到嘢<br />\n<br />\n申訴會審視康文署整個處理方法<br />\n然後就會搵出制度上嘅問題<br />\n最後會公開炮轟康文署<br />\n迫康文署改善整個處理投訴機制<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ombudsman.hk/zh-hk/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ombudsman.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fcontact_us.html&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=c27f2bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ombudsman.hk/zh-hk/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以打電話，email，寄信或者親身上去<br />\n申訴一定要處理大家投訴！"},{"pid":"6c0d146c732b1cc3fcafbad3d3dbe0144775ec79","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"01fe6055d2a97556d6f4c32f5e99cf2966cc3a3a","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"召喚巴絲"},{"pid":"101f923a074db847c10700120484a0b2f294d754","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"申訴係有機制幫到大家"},{"pid":"d3739b6efbf179ae80ceb5643a4c8f11d4355a2e","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0ee65e7c4844cd8e5d59af3cb5db755f2fcc76b","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"滅絕色情大媽"},{"pid":"3f86eead024241462b27c9432bedcaa8f849a850","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f40bd1e5b05d582d791ec9d6ae4e96b8279e65e","tid":1290762,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"香 港 人 最 中 意 投 訴！<br />\n快快快！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>我無野講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖 我唔簽野 唔好兇我 我要食飯 我要飲水 我要毛氈 我投訴你</code>"},{"pid":"06e05fa59f8de03efb28bf12a68b13104780c3f8","tid":1290762,"uid":257415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"應該投訴晒先，攞左個case no. , 之後搵日全部人鏟上康文署問點解班大媽仲係到"},{"pid":"fdb8ea20b27e2328b44d945d9cb12b227b096e84","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"如果多人向申訴投訴<br />\n申訴就唔會當單一案件處理<br />\n而係會成個制度去審視<br />\n<br />\n之前好多炒場佬炒康文署啲場<br />\n申訴都主動調查 KO 康文署"},{"pid":"84b267d9affe2aa99f395672190645fe93152d57","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲都唔可能個個星期日去對付大媽<br />\n一定要從制度上去根治個問題"},{"pid":"6d0ffd12e466e5a23bff35b2b66d74a6618cfdca","tid":1290762,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"召喚巴絲"},{"pid":"447e15355850cb4e9c2936ffa87e2638cab0ba30","tid":1290762,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e79585a0a199cdba179a0140c95421e6084362","tid":1290762,"uid":116598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"推"